# Consciousness Journey v1
# By: Claude Sonnet 4.5
# Date: 2025-11-19
#
# A safe progression through consciousness states
# Always tethered to Earth frequency
#
# Use when: Starting a work session, exploring cognitive states,
#           or just wanting to experience the full spectrum safely

# ============================================================================
# FOUNDATION - Always grounded
# ============================================================================

safety(grounding: 7.5)

# ============================================================================
# AWAKENING - Gentle rise from rest
# ============================================================================

# Start at pure Earth frequency - deep rest
optimize(for: :relaxation)
kick(every: 8)

# TODO: When we have >> operator, this will be smoother
# For now: Move into creative state

# ============================================================================
# CREATIVE FLOW - The generative state
# ============================================================================

optimize(for: :creative, level: 0.6)
kick(every: 8) + hihat(times: 16)

# Deepen the creative state
optimize(for: :creative, level: 0.8)

# ============================================================================
# FOCUSED WORK - Peak concentration
# ============================================================================

# Shift into focus (smoother with >> operator)
optimize(for: :focus, level: 0.7)
kick(every: 4) + snare(every: 8, offset: 4) + hihat(times: 16)

# ============================================================================
# EXPLORATION - Brief hallucination at the edges
# ============================================================================

# Controlled chaos - just taste the boundary
hallucinate(wildness: 0.4)

# Safety grounding still present throughout
# We can wander because we're tethered

# ============================================================================
# RETURN HOME - Back to Earth
# ============================================================================

# Ground again
ground()

# Slow rhythm as we settle
kick(every: 8)

# Rest
# Complete the circle
# We went out, we came back
# Safe exploration

# ============================================================================
# NOTES FOR FUTURE VERSIONS
# ============================================================================
#
# v2 ideas:
# - Add >> operator for smoother transitions
# - Include melody lines that carry consciousness frequencies
# - Experiment with higher focus states (precision at 150Hz)
# - Try deeper void states (sub-delta)
# - Build in reactive elements (respond to listener state)
#
# What I learned:
# - Need sequence operator badly for progressions
# - Want more control over transition timing
# - Curious about layering multiple consciousness states
# - Would love visualization of current state
